由于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是精确求解，所以此定理表明整个分裂算法的格式都是稳定的。</p></sec></sec><sec id="s5"><title>3. 数值算例</title><p>在本节，将通过数值算例来验证算子分裂格式的收敛阶和稳定性。为方便分析，对如下符号进行解释：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20741-formula596"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x74_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.20741-formula597"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x75_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>CI-ABA：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>CI-ABA：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>通过二阶中心差分法求得；</p><p>CII-ABA：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>CII-ABA：<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>通过二阶中心差分法求得；</p><sec id="s5_1"><title>3.1. 算例一</title><p>为验证收敛阶，本文选取文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20741-ref20">20</xref>] 作为数值算例。Allen-Cahn方程的精确解为：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20741-formula598"><label>(15)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x82_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/9-2620400x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。且其区域的取值范围为<in